%^CYAN%^Psions%^RESET%^ are able to select a discipline that represents their inner nature.

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^Be aware%^RESET%^ - You can change your discipline once every three weeks with the
'discipline' command.

%^CYAN%^Discipline specific spells and feats are listed in their respective help files:%^RESET%^

